 - Add budgie-weathershow
 - Add budgie-recentlyused; it is a vala based applet
 - budgie-hotcorners and quicknote rewritten in vala
 - wpreviews - fix crash on some occasions
 - showtime - fix crash on early exit
v0.5.0 Hop Hop
